snippet.title: Trouble of Tabu - Official Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Hey everyone! Thanks for tuning in to catch the first glimpse of Trouble of Tabu! As a solo developer pouring heart and soul into this project, I'm thrilled to share a taste of what's to come. Crafting a game entirely independently and self-publishing comes with its challenges, but it also means every bit of support counts.

If you're as excited about this adventure as I am, adding Trouble of Tabu to your wishlist means the world to me! Your interest fuels the journey ahead.

Got questions or simply want to chat about the game? Swing by Discord—I'm all ears and eager to connect with fellow gamers!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1950530/Trouble_of_Tabu/?beta=1
Discord: https://discord.gg/u9bGAmEn52
Website: https://above-games.com
